        "TileImage": "$($repository 95bfa85f-d47e-48a6-aaa2-f118a9eec0df).Image",
        "Description": "Ollie: Quick sidetrack from you main objective. The Erasers have been gearing up for a war on you. So if you wanna keep things quiet, you&apos;ll have to put the plans to a halt. Gun down their best guys and we should be clear. I highly recommend bringing a sniper rifle of some kind and doming them from the water tower, but hey, only a suggestion. Once you deal with these guys, off to Japan you go. Hey... I&apos;ve been wondering. Do you feel guilt? There *were* some unecessary deaths on this journey...",
